Package: SinCE
Type: Package
Title: An interactive shinyapp for the analysing and visaulizing of scRNA data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Xiaofan(Ashley) Zhao
Maintainer: Xiaofan(Ashley) Zhao <zhao343@usc.edu>
Description: Basing on Saurat and Plotly, SinCE is an interface that help you load single cell expression matrix and run data perform QC, clustering and gene expression analysis in an interactive manner. You can also set costumize group information and downlowd label files of inteteted cells.
    This tool is still under development, any suggestions would be extremely welcomed :)
